name: gymme - free landing page
description:
A trouble-free gym landing page created for prospective junior frontend developers who may need an example design project that allows them to practice their skills.


Figma structure:

-> 🚀 Getting Started - an intro page.

-> ⚙️ Style Guide - a specification for reusable elements of the design.

-> 🎨 Design - the actual design, including three different breakpoints and mobile navigation.

-> 🌁 Cover Image - just a thumbnail for the Figma app. You can use it as a social image (og-image) though.


Duplicate, develop & have fun! 🤟🏼
